    "category": "reference",
    "section": "api",
    "order": 300,
    "content": "\n# RetryOptions\n\n## Properties\n\n| Name | Type | Description |\n|------|------|-------------|\n| `retries` | `number` | Maximum number of retry attempts |\n| `minTimeout` | `number` | Base delay in milliseconds (doubles each retry) |\n| `maxTimeout` | `number` | Maximum delay in milliseconds |\n| `factor` | `number` | Multiplier for exponential backoff |\n| `randomize` | `boolean` | Whether to add random jitter to delays |\n| `shouldRetry` | `reflection` | Custom function to determine if error is retriable |\n\n",
    "code": "\n# RetryOptions\n\n## Properties\n\n| Name | Type | Description |\n|------|------|-------------|\n| `retries` | `number` | Maximum number of retry attempts |\n| `minTimeout` | `number` | Base delay in milliseconds (doubles each retry) |\n| `maxTimeout` | `number` | Maximum delay in milliseconds |\n| `factor` | `number` | Multiplier for exponential backoff |\n| `randomize` | `boolean` | Whether to add random jitter to delays |\n| `shouldRetry` | `reflection` | Custom function to determine if error is retriable |\n\n",
